*耍流氓，威脅吃免錢的。或拒不付帳。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-tw | publisher = | title =天下沒有白吃的大餐，女子吃完霸王餐，遭警方逮捕！ | url =http://www.justlaw.com.tw/News01.php?id=851 | author = | date = | accessdate =2009-12-15 | archive-date =2017-11-21 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171121021234/http://justlaw.com.tw/News01.php?id=851 | dead-url =no }}</ref>
*用完餐才称沒錢支付餐點消費，拒绝结账。<ref>{{cite web| language = zh-cn | title = 吃了一顿“霸王餐” 换来拘留十五天 | url = http://he.news.cn/society/2021-12/16/c_1128164423.htm | accessdate = 2022-05-07 | author =  | date = 2021-12-16 | format = HTML | work = [[新华网|新华网]]河北 | publisher = 石家庄日报 | archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20220507143602/http://he.news.cn/society/2021-12/16/c_1128164423.htm | archivedate = 2022-05-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*明知無力支付卻故意大量點餐。
*共食餐點時，每次用完餐後假裝沒事，總有一天付款人會忘記收費。

